<div id="header">
<h1>mGTK</h1>
</div>
<div id="content">
<div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p><a href="http://mgtk.sourceforge.net/">mGTK</a> is a wrapper for
<a href="http://www.gtk.org/">GTK+</a>, a GUI toolkit.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>We recommend using mGTK 0.93, which is not listed on their home page,
but is available at the
<a href="http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=23226&amp;package_id=16523">file
release page</a>.  To test it, after unpacking, do <code>cd examples; make
mlton</code>, after which you should be able to run the many examples
(<code>signup-mlton</code>, <code>listview-mlton</code>, &#8230;&#8203;).</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
